    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. but \"necessary investment\" sounds pretty subjective. can u dive deeper into the actual costs vs the benefits? i mean, how much of the \"long-term savings\" is actually proven vs just theoretical? i'm hearing a lot of local owners say they're just gonna struggle to keep up with the compliance costs.",
